name: Carpeye
description:
Part of a project for a birthday present for my ecdysis. "Carpeye" was created with limited vision and is part of my challenge to see what I can trade this for to build a modest tiny NFT collection to get my ecdysis into NFTs. I promised her whatever NFTs I can trade for before 9/5/21 are hers for her birthday. On that day every copy that isn't traded for will be burnt. One going to her, of course.

30 year since coming out of yamum'z cunt celebration!
